data.description: Beautifully updated home on quiet cul-de-sac.  Lots of new throughout, including new HVAC, exterior and interior paint, some flooring, windows, sliding door, front door, storm door, fireplace tile and mantle, interior lights, exterior lights, garage storage units, kitchen countertops, fence, drainage, and the list goes on.  Don't miss out on this gem.
